// ═══════════════════ ROBUST INTRABAR EXIT SYSTEM ═══════════════════
// Exit logic that works properly while preventing alert spam
// Key insight: strategy.exit() calls must run every bar, only alerts should be limited

// ──────── 1. MA EXIT (Intrabar with Anti-Spam) ────────────
